title: Better With Two
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2Mv3GY1

by ivyspinners

“The Alliance might lose her again when she’s back,” Jyn said. “Knowing your administration.”

He snorted. “They might. She won’t let them.”

The best couples don’t judge each other. They judge other people together.
